# 🔥 Dijkstra vs Bellman-Ford

| Feature                  | Dijkstra   | Bellman-Ford |
| ------------------------ | ---------- | ------------ |
| Negative Weights         | ❌ No       | ✅ Yes        |
| Faster                   | ✅ Yes      | ❌ Slower     |
| Time Complexity          | O(E log V) | O(VE)        |
| Negative Cycle Detection | ❌ No       | ✅ Yes        |

